articles.description: Mathematically, Pakistan can still qualify for the World Cup 2023 semi-finals but they would need a lot of results to go their way. | Cricket
articles.content: This is a familiar territory for Pakistan. Down, but not out, hoping for a 1992-esque comeback and relying on things to magically fall their way. Babar Azam and his men were among the title contender… [+2261 chars]
